data.meta_description: Swedengfdgf - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Sweden is a Scandinavian country located in Northern Europe. It has a total population of over 9.8 million and has a land area of 450,295 square kilometers, making it the third largest country in the European Union. Sweden has a long history dating back to prehistoric times and emerged as a unified and independent country during the Middle Ages. It expanded into a major European power during the 17th century but lost territories over subsequent centuries. Sweden maintains a Nordic social welfare system and ranks highly on quality of life and human development indicators.
